      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute dream and has been meticulously cared for\u2014honestly, it\u2019s in pristine, mint condition! It drives beautifully and looks even better in person. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this gem. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
