    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a masterfully preserved E46 M3, powered by the S54B32 high-revving inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with the critical rod bearing service and subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate selection, channeling torque through a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with zero bushing deflection, while the exterior finish displays zero orange peel or clear coat failure. Inside, the Nappa leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster compression. This is a collector-grade vehicle optimized for peak thermal efficiency and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 43500.0,
