    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2011 BMW M3 Coupe (E92) in Alpine White over Fox Red Novillo leather. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since new. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its factory deep gloss with no swirl marks, stone chips, or scratches; it has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. The interior is equally pristine, with the leather remaining matte and supple, showing absolutely no bolster wear or discoloration. All carbon fiber trim pieces are free of yellowing or cracks, and every electronic component\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates as intended. Mechanically, the car is perfect. It features a complete, documented service history from authorized BMW technicians. The S65 V8 engine runs smoothly, the DCT transmission shifts crisply, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean with no signs of fluid leaks or corrosion. It rides on original ZCP Competition wheels with brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a high-performance icon that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Clean title and two sets of keys included.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
