    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring an impeccable service history and an interior and exterior preserved to an exacting standard. It is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled mechanical and aesthetic integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
