      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it literally just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it really shows. Not a single scratch or dent, and the interior still has that fresh, new-car smell. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be thrilled. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
