    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S65 4.0L V8 engine. The powerplant remains in peak operating condition, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) offers crisp, lightning-fast shifts, while the variable M-differential lock ensures surgical power distribution. The chassis retains its factory-fresh rigidity, with the EDC (Electronic Damper Control) and suspension geometry showing zero signs of fatigue or bushing wear. Every mechanical component, from the VANOS system to the subframe reinforcements, has been preserved to exacting standards. This is a collector-grade vehicle with an unblemished undercarriage and a flawless service pedigree, offering a pure, unadulterated driving experience.",
